-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Additional Notice (Medical / Clinical Use)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This software is a research and educational demonstration of a few-shot
learning pipeline (Prototypical Networks + Grad-CAM) for retinal image
analysis. It ships with a procedurally generated synthetic demo support set
and an untrained CNN encoder. IT IS NOT A CERTIFIED OR VALIDATED MEDICAL
DEVICE, and it must not be used, in whole or in part, for real clinical
diagnosis, treatment decisions, or patient care without proper validation,
regulatory clearance, and review by qualified medical professionals.